@startuml 设备注册用例鲁棒图

skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam roundcorner 5
skinparam shadowing false

left to right direction

actor "学校管理员" as Admin

boundary "设备注册界面" as Boundary
control "设备注册" as Controller
entity "设备信息" as DeviceEntity
entity "设备表" as DeviceTable

Admin --> Boundary : 填写设备信息\n点击注册
Boundary --> Controller : 提交设备信息
Controller --> DeviceEntity : 创建设备对象
Controller --> DeviceTable : 保存设备信息
DeviceTable --> Controller : 返回保存结果
Controller --> Boundary : 返回注册结果
Boundary --> Admin : 显示注册成功

note right of Controller
  业务逻辑：
  1. 验证设备信息
  2. 生成设备ID
  3. 设置默认状态
  4. 保存到数据库
end note

@enduml




